          <LEXSenses>
            <LEXSense LanguageCode="en" LastEdited="2021-08-30 14:54:03" LastEditedBy="">
              <DefinitionLong/>
              <DefinitionShort>to spend completely, with the implication of uselessly, and therefore, to waste</DefinitionShort>
              <Glosses>
                <Gloss>to spend completely</Gloss>
                <Gloss>to waste</Gloss>
              </Glosses>
              <Comments>In some languages ‘to waste’ may be expressed as ‘to use up and to get no benefit’ or ‘to have, but for no purpose.’</Comments>
